Package: BTYDplus
Type: Package
Title: Extension of R Package BTYD
Version: 0.7.0
Date: 2016-04-19
Authors@R: person("Michael", "Platzer", email = "michael.platzer@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Extends the functionality of BTYD package by providing methods for
    parameter estimation and scoring for NBD, G/G/NBD, MBG/NBD, BG/CNBD-k and
    MBG/CNBD-k models, as well as MCMC samples for Pareto/NBD,
    Abe's Pareto/NBD variant and Pareto/GGG.
URL: https://github.com/mplatzer/BTYDplus
BugReports: https://github.com/mplatzer/BTYDplus/issues
License: GPL-3
LinkingTo: Rcpp
Depends: R (>= 3.2.0)
Imports:
    Rcpp,
    BTYD (>= 2.3),
    coda,
    data.table,
    mvtnorm,
    bayesm
Suggests: 
    testthat,
    gsl
Roxygen: list(wrap = FALSE)
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
LazyData: true
